summary: An ordinance relating to the Water Dept. and providing for the sale and conveyance of certain City (Water Dept.) property in Section 1, Township 22 North, Range 5 East, W.M., Section 36, Township 23 North, Range 5 East, W.M., and Section 6, Township 22 North, Range 6 East, W.M., to King County for road purposes.
